flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[User runs CLI command]

    B --> C[CLI parses arguments]
    C --> D[Load runner config]

    D --> E[Initialize BackendRegistry]
    E --> F[Register SubprocessBackend]
    F --> G[Register DockerBackend]

    G --> H[Initialize ReporterRegistry]
    H --> I[Register ConsoleReporter]
    I --> J[Register AnalyticsReporter]

    J --> K[RunnerBuilder receives config and registries]
    K --> L[Select backend from BackendRegistry]
    L --> M[Select reporters from ReporterRegistry]
    M --> N[Build Runner]

    N --> O[TestDiscovery discovers test files]
    O --> P{Any tests found?}

    P -- No --> Q[Print no tests found]
    Q --> Z([End])

    P -- Yes --> R[Create ExecutionRequest list]
    R --> S[ParallelExecutor executes requests]

    S --> T[Selected Backend executes each request]
    T --> U[Collect ExecutionResult list]

    U --> V[ResultAggregator creates Summary]
    V --> W[Each Reporter prints result or analytics]

    W --> X{Any failed tests?}
    X -- Yes --> Y[Print failed test details]
    X -- No --> AA[Print all tests passed]

    Y --> Z([End])
    AA --> Z([End])
